response.original_title: Diana: The People's Princess 20 Years On
response.overview: Two decades after the death of Diana, Princess of Wales, the mere mention of her name is able to provoke emotion, reflection, and a flood of memories of a special person who formed a very special place in all of our hearts. In this hour long film we remind ourselves of her origins, how she overcame a childhood of distant parents and shyness to become a superstar, known throughout the world.
response.title: Diana: The People's Princess 20 Years On
